# FormSubmit.co Configuration
# Contact form uses FormSubmit.co (no API key required)
# Email is hardcoded in src/components/Contact.jsx
#
# To change the recipient email:
# 1. Update FORMSUBMIT_EMAIL in src/components/Contact.jsx
# 2. First-time setup: submit the form once, then check your inbox
#    for a FormSubmit.co confirmation email and click the activation link
#
# Email templates are in public/email-templates/
# - auto-reply.html        -> sent to the visitor (auto-response)
# - owner-notification.html -> sent to you (the site owner)
